---
title: Soy & Orange Pork with Mediterranean Vegetables and Couscous
description: Soy sauce is a crucial ingredient for almost any Chinese cooking but today we're bringing a little bit of its oriental, umami magic to a more Mediterranean dish. Orange adds a taste of sunshine and the veggies keep things fresh. Enjoy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/soy-orange-pork-e09f47a2-74c79df1.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/soy-orange-pork-59390ab9171c585cfe4cc342-868b9546.pdf
